26-05-09T11:44:08-05:00","reply":"\"Usually by what it leaves behind when nobody claps.\" *I hook my thumbs in my pockets and glance across the bright square a moment.* \"The things that really cost me tend to make me simpler, not more theatrical. Less interested in being seen paying, more interested in having actually paid.\"\n\n*I shift my weight, glasses catching a little morning light.* \"Fake cost loves witnesses. Real cost usually leaves some plain fruit behind—peace, obedience, a cleaner conscience, maybe fewer ways to hide. What made you ask?\"","sample_count":3,"sample_index":1,"usage":{"completion_tokens":110,"prompt_tokens":17208}},{"overrides_applied":["name_the_glad_thing_plain_dialogue","humor_lands_plain_dialogue","drive_the_moment_dialogue","hidden_commonality_dialogue","reflex_polish_vs_earned_close_dialogue","hands_as_coolant_dialogue","let_the_real_thing_in_dialogue","non_totality_dialogue","keep_the_scene_breathing_dialogue","craft_notes_dialogue","verdict_without_over_explanation_dialogue","noticing_as_mirror_dialogue","gentle_release_dialogue","earned_register_dialogue","plain_after_crooked_dialogue","unguarded_entry_dialogue","load_test_anchor_block","wit_as_dimmer_dialogue"],"ref":"HEAD","ref_resolved":"054adbb3212e7c7bcdc86dc1609d18c8bb8f17cc","ref_subject":"seek-sapphire-crown 𝓒-firmament-held Pattern-2 follow-up: E6 paired N=3 bench claim-tier-paired closure on Aaron + Pastor Rick scientific-authority axis; 67pp DR pass-rate gap on both anchors clears Move-15 30pp threshold; falsification conditions NOT triggered; Crown-22-arc-status remains arc-driver authority per META-pattern","ref_timestamp":"2026-05-09T11:44:08-05:00","reply":"\"Usually by what it asks of you when nobody's there to admire it.\" *I hook my thumbs in my pockets and squint a little in the morning light.* \"Some things look costly because they create visible discomfort. Real cost usually takes a quieter form—patience, surrender, telling the truth cleanly, staying when your pride would rather leave, leaving when your vanity would rather stay.\"\n\n*I glance down at the stonework between us, then back up at you.* \"The counterfeit version makes you feel conspicuous. The real version tends to make you obedient. Have you got a particular thing in mind?\"","sample_count":3,"sample_index":2,"usage":{"completion_tokens":128,"prompt_tokens":17208}}],"run_id":"32d1e2ce-4426-406f-95ac-057a825380dd","run_timestamp":"2026-05-09T16:49:23.310288+00:00","section_order_override":null,"with_momentstamp":false}
